text: Erest of elde dich above stibbe þanne endlang weies on strete so bi strete on holedene endlang denes.
To springwellen þanen to olde Gore so on cleyate on þe elde stibbe.
Þanen on olde burgh suthward of þare berwe in on þe foulle lake on thone bithe of þan bithe in on thone welle bi este foxcotone.
Of þan welle west on þone mer aker of þan acre endlang weies eft to þe olde dich.
